formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) Construction work of the project is completed and project Architect / Engineer have already issued 100% completion  certificate in Form-1 and Form-2 respectively. 

2) The promoter has deposited 100% of money received from allottees in RERA account (as Kalupur Commercial Co. Op. Bank
does not open separate RERA collection and retention accounts), accordingly for the purpose of certifying amount withdrawn
from RERA account till date in Sr. No. 7, we have considered only 70% of total amount received from the allottees as rest 30%
was not required to be deposited in RERA account.

3) The promoter have paid secured construction loan from The Kalupur Commercial Co. Op. Bank in full and mortgage on project land and units are released by the bank by way of Release Deed which is uploaded herewith.
